item.description:
Weather disclaimer - read the posts as we get closer. We're starting at 530 but being late is ok. WE'll go to Marc Anthony's at about 730 if you want to join us there.

PLEASE READ THE DIRECTIONS - CALL OR EMAIL WITH QUESTIONS

We are playing on Shell Point Beach in Onset. It isnt on my GPS so I found a good address on Google Maps - 59 West Central Avenue, Onset, MA.   When you get to the end of West Central Ave take a left and your first right down to the parking lot on the beach. That's where we will be playing.

Any questions call me - 508-479-7690

We'll start at 530 but come later if you can.

We'll meet rain or shine.

AFTER VOLLEYBALL - we'll keep it simple and to to Marc Anthonys I have a crazy week ahead.

in case of weather cancellation - we'll meet at Mar Anthony's

see you there - R
item.how_to_find_us: look for the volleyball net on the beach
